        "TileImage": "$($repository 52d3a356-dd04-468f-88ca-7441d9baff1e).Image",
        "Description": "Some Kronsdant Employees have been, you guessed it, smuggling explosives through shipments of supplies. To do this they used their cheif mechanic, cheif scientist, head of security, and some other security members to ensure it runs smoothly. Shut down the operation. Eliminate All Targets.",
